{"tid":1291937,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"回應 4 青年輕生　陳日君哽咽落淚　望珍惜生命　「我哋需要佢哋」","createTime":"2019-07-07T05:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T06:26:46.000Z","uid":48083,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c072aca07e66672c56a2437775ab510dd92c9c79","tid":1291937,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:55:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uDsFwmg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuDsFwmg.png&h=35654bcb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/skcVkeD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FskcVkeD.png&h=0af41141&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「612 人道支援基金」今天正式宣布成立，並取代原來於 6 月 16 日臨時成立的「反送中受傷被捕者人道支援基金」。基金信託人為天主教香港教區榮休主教陳日君樞機、吳靄儀、許寶強、何秀蘭、何韻詩。取名「612」是認為該天有標<ins>誌性的重大意義，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但基金的支援對象不限於 6 月 12 日當天的參與者，而是包括所有反送中運動中受傷、被捕或相關人士。</ins></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n陳日君在記者會上被記者問及社會充斥負面情緒，已有四位年輕人輕生，我們有何出路時，他一度語塞，未能即時回應，其後在回答時哽咽落淚。<br />\n<br />\n「激到人民咁憤怒的人應該負責任」<br />\n<br />\n陳日君指任何人，無論是年輕人抑或老人家，無論有何人生，都會珍惜每一個人的生命。年輕人被逼到用這樣的方法去表達傷心和失望，是這個社會的羞恥，「激到人民咁憤怒的人應該負責任」。<br />\n<br />\n說到未有機會阻止他們輕生時，陳日君哽咽落淚。<br />\n<br />\n陳日君強調，教會絕對反對人如此浪費自己的生命，因為每一個生命都好寶貴，他們如在，就多一個聲音與大家一起，所他們不應該輕生，「我哋需要佢哋」，他希望人人回到最基本，珍惜每一個人的生命，最基本人的本性，希望不會再有人輕生，「沒有需要，太多了，希望大家振作起來，團結一致，用和平的方法，也對自己和平」。<br />\n<br />\n陳日君又指，今次事件政府應該負很大的責任，特赦被捕示威者是應該的，「在這麼多人出來遊行後，政府的反應出奇地不適當。所以我們多謝這些年輕人，希望政府不會在他們身上，懲罰我們，或者為了我們懲罰年輕人，希望社會有公義的看法。」  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/回應-4-青年輕生-陳日君哽咽落淚-望珍惜生命-我哋需要佢哋/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89-4-%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E7%94%9F-%E9%99%B3%E6%97%A5%E5%90%9B%E5%93%BD%E5%92%BD%E8%90%BD%E6%B7%9A-%E6%9C%9B%E7%8F%8D%E6%83%9C%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD-%E6%88%91%E5%93%8B%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E4%BD%A2%E5%93%8B%2F&d=o%2Fu7L%2BZntrZWbswpyROzR7TyP%2F9hhZoMZuVNmYF6dao%3D&h=e2651b72\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89-4-%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E7%94%9F-%E9%99%B3%E6%97%A5%E5%90%9B%E5%93%BD%E5%92%BD%E8%90%BD%E6%B7%9A-%E6%9C%9B%E7%8F%8D%E6%83%9C%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD-%E6%88%91%E5%93%8B%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E4%BD%A2%E5%93%8B%2F&h=670e04b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/回應-4-青年輕生-陳日君哽咽落淚-望珍惜生命-我哋需要佢哋/</a>"},{"pid":"22339203b15c5e835894c40e27b5d04388c1579d","tid":1291937,"uid":36008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:57:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f82f4564ec5ad0e7ea136f196047adf2902a06","tid":1291937,"uid":48631,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:58:53.000Z","msg":"陳日君真係香港天主教嘅良心"},{"pid":"166060132cf39bad575ad7bc2cf8bf0718b764ce","tid":1291937,"uid":107201,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"90f82f4564ec5ad0e7ea136f196047adf2902a06","tid":1291937,"uid":48631,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:58:53.000Z","msg":"陳日君真係香港天主教嘅良心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T06:02:57.000Z","msg":"林鄭係全世界天主教徒既恥辱"},{"pid":"97c0d872d1f65177da2ea525b504b11701efbfde","tid":1291937,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T06:05:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e51b0bfecfe19d57f20505050c279acb866f7f4","tid":1291937,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T06:08:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"743045c98db661a59ec97fa3bb8c4548396f4aae","tid":1291937,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike